id panel-has-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;row_stretch&quot;:&quot;full&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;,&quot;align&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;background_image&quot;:&quot;288&quot;,&quot;overlay&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;overlay_color&quot;:&quot;#000000&quot;}\" ><div class=\"siteorigin-panels-stretch panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-87-1\" style=\"background-image: url(http://www.localhost/fco/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/b30e4fbc6d54ebe73ebbc5b12709d6a6.jpg);padding: 100px 0; \" data-stretch-type=\"full\" data-hasbg=\"hasbg\" data-overlay=\"true\" data-overlay-color=\"#000000\" ><div id=\"pgc-87-1-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"1\" ><div id=\"panel-87-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;content_alignment&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;title_color&quot;:&quot;#999999&quot;,&quot;headings_color&quot;:&quot;#443f3f&quot;}\" ><div style=\"text-align: left;\" data-title-color=\"#999999\" data-headings-color=\"#443f3f\" class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-87-1-0-0\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">The Only Difference Between your Business and Top Businesses is EXPOSURE</h3><div class=\"textwidget\"><h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #999999;\">Think about it.  How many times have you been at a show where you cannot believe the incrdible talent.  You ask, how is this group not famous!?  In your heart of hearts you know its because they don\'t get the exposure.  This is why we are so exited to work with small businesses, because we just have so much to offer them.  So much value to give. </span></h4><h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #999999;\">Once you realize this, how could you wait one more second to pull the trigger.  Meet with us, your first week is FREE!  See how bright your future can be.</span></h4></div></d